column143: participantComments:"Since Purple and Yellow worked together to harvest the center trees on the first two rounds
column144: that did influence my answer that I thought they did have an unspoken agreement to harvest the center tree together but perhaps not 100% of the time. The fact that the center tree gives 8 berries to each farmer whether they harvest together or not also influenced my answers. I answered that I did not think Purple would feel much guilt going to a different tree and that Yellow wouldn't be too angry if Purple went to a different tree because I was told they were given 8 berries each by the center tree whether they harvest together or not. "
